elements.name: Verify user able to place order in Open Cart application

embeddings.name: Verify user able to place order in Open Cart application

steps.name: user is on Open Cart home page
user navigate to Open Cart login page from MyAccount flyout
user login with username "app.username" and password "app.password"
Open Cart account page should open
user navigate to Open Cart home page from account page
user clicks Add to cart button
Open Cart product detail page should open
user add product to shopping cart
user navigate to Open Cart shopping cart page from product view drop
Open Cart shopping cart page should open
user verify the product details in shopping cart
